  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1239260/extras/59b068723ef12b32c23c0cbb4917a724.avif?t=1742064995\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1239260/extras/43e467f09e6b33e9c20cc9b8f1b68283.avif?t=1742064995\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1239260/extras/958029a7becd616568e3c76b57ba6654.avif?t=1742064995\" width=600 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1239260/extras/8fe63a00c6bbfe600b8142e4f339eb38.avif?t=1742064995\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Barro F is the new sequel for the game Barro, faster then ever before.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 11 new cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 new race tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Single player or 4 players local split screen </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > New and improved time trial mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Up to 10 cars on the grid</p></li></ul>",
